        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Robocall Enforcement Enhancement Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill extends the statute of limitations for enforcing robocall violations and authorizes the Federal Communications Commission to pursue violations of robocall rules without first issuing a citation. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
